{"tid":803882,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（科學）舉證責任問題","createTime":"2018-09-02T15:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T09:46:23.000Z","uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b7925de3a1ad33ec6c2343850d979972bdba969d","tid":803882,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:11:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3SIaeSEQSWE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3SIaeSEQSWE&d=d86UGvFreZP%2FNpga7V2Jd0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=5bb3345c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3SIaeSEQSWE</a><br />\n<br />\n假設<br />\n我哋返返去事發當日，一睇到呢條片，我哋就會話朱蛇攬權亂咁打人<br />\n但係藍絲就會質疑當事人 唔係單純路過/犯咗法，所以朱蛇打佢係合理合法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁呢個case個舉證責任係邊個度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96de24afa5c1fa20d44c8cb4be937d5bb6123dd","tid":803882,"uid":88663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:32:02.000Z","msg":"真心求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442d946509b8f2e8de46146edcd7a96d63bc5d56","tid":803882,"uid":200202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:39:00.000Z","msg":"喺佢地兩個到"},{"pid":"4a04468023ea4b145f9d8f376f8a19f717d9057c","tid":803882,"uid":200202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"442d946509b8f2e8de46146edcd7a96d63bc5d56","tid":803882,"uid":200202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:39:00.000Z","msg":"喺佢地兩個到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:39:42.000Z","msg":"兩邊都有責任"},{"pid":"a1199faea58457638a4c8c83b86046ed874bd415","tid":803882,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"442d946509b8f2e8de46146edcd7a96d63bc5d56","tid":803882,"uid":200202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:39:00.000Z","msg":"喺佢地兩個到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:40:49.000Z","msg":"即係兩個講法都要prove?<br />\n邊個prove唔到就唔可信？"},{"pid":"66678f8e360fc87bd36a8379cc2a45b4e6c96714","tid":803882,"uid":199716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:42:57.000Z","msg":"責任係控方囉<br />\n如果係吿個警察打人咪搵證據證明佢用棍打無辜嘅途人 <br />\n如果係吿個途人其實有心搞事咪搵證據證明佢係滋事份子/阻差辦公"},{"pid":"cbfcfb52e356fda13ab43d11afff290b94f8ac9c","tid":803882,"uid":200202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a1199faea58457638a4c8c83b86046ed874bd415","tid":803882,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"442d946509b8f2e8de46146edcd7a96d63bc5d56","tid":803882,"uid":200202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:39:00.000Z","msg":"喺佢地兩個到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:40:49.000Z","msg":"即係兩個講法都要prove?<br />\n邊個prove唔到就唔可信？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:43:38.000Z","msg":"係，因為你睇條片只可以講到警察打人呢個事實，你話佢亂打或者有苦衷都係條片以外嘅野"},{"pid":"31f8992b54361c0c7eb388a5eb45b8957c3af38e","tid":803882,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:00:16.000Z","msg":"你想講日常定法庭先？<br />\n唔可以混為一談 <br />\n<br />\n法庭就你拎條片出來做證據告人  <br />\n梗係要證明條片冇修改 冇剪走d重要事件 <br />\n但法庭以外嘅情況  <br />\n本身已經有七警打人呢d事出現之下<br />\n一般人根據呢條片 先相信係警犬亂打人 就好合理 <br />\n<br />\n正如法庭告唔入某報商販毒  唔代表一般人相信佢販毒係唔合理"},{"pid":"a8959ac249ca724f3a9d8747384274b421284aa9","tid":803882,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"就算犯左法都唔係打佢的理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非佢做出某d需要使用武力制服的行為"},{"pid":"3ab61854b4309999ee97e5c432737fbcb86a27bc","tid":803882,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cbfcfb52e356fda13ab43d11afff290b94f8ac9c","tid":803882,"uid":200202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a1199faea58457638a4c8c83b86046ed874bd415","tid":803882,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"442d946509b8f2e8de46146edcd7a96d63bc5d56","tid":803882,"uid":200202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:39:00.000Z","msg":"喺佢地兩個到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:40:49.000Z","msg":"即係兩個講法都要prove?<br />\n邊個prove唔到就唔可信？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:43:38.000Z","msg":"係，因為你睇條片只可以講到警察打人呢個事實，你話佢亂打或者有苦衷都係條片以外嘅野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:25:50.000Z","msg":"即係當日我同人講警察打人，我show呢條片俾佢睇嘅話我已經盡左我嘅舉證責任？<br />\n當有藍絲質疑條片假/ 當事人唔係單純路過，個舉證責任就係個藍絲度？"},{"pid":"182c6fd607b75e7f276bc4e89f8b8bd805a0c682","tid":803882,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31f8992b54361c0c7eb388a5eb45b8957c3af38e","tid":803882,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:00:16.000Z","msg":"你想講日常定法庭先？<br />\n唔可以混為一談 <br />\n<br />\n法庭就你拎條片出來做證據告人  <br />\n梗係要證明條片冇修改 冇剪走d重要事件 <br />\n但法庭以外嘅情況  <br />\n本身已經有七警打人呢d事出現之下<br />\n一般人根據呢條片 先相信係警犬亂打人 就好合理 <br />\n<br />\n正如法庭告唔入某報商販毒  唔代表一般人相信佢販毒係唔合理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:30:58.000Z","msg":"七警打人同埋呢單有因果關係咩？"},{"pid":"eb4fcd3b43973f2e9490d489dae9ee5c2cd69959","tid":803882,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"182c6fd607b75e7f276bc4e89f8b8bd805a0c682","tid":803882,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31f8992b54361c0c7eb388a5eb45b8957c3af38e","tid":803882,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:00:16.000Z","msg":"你想講日常定法庭先？<br />\n唔可以混為一談 <br />\n<br />\n法庭就你拎條片出來做證據告人  <br />\n梗係要證明條片冇修改 冇剪走d重要事件 <br />\n但法庭以外嘅情況  <br />\n本身已經有七警打人呢d事出現之下<br />\n一般人根據呢條片 先相信係警犬亂打人 就好合理 <br />\n<br />\n正如法庭告唔入某報商販毒  唔代表一般人相信佢販毒係唔合理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:30:58.000Z","msg":"七警打人同埋呢單有因果關係咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:54:14.000Z","msg":"咁都唔明？<br />\n警察有前科  d人會傾向相信佢地不合理地使用武力"},{"pid":"15aa7b63b3aa6700ac1042852c8444437edacf3a","tid":803882,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb4fcd3b43973f2e9490d489dae9ee5c2cd69959","tid":803882,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"182c6fd607b75e7f276bc4e89f8b8bd805a0c682","tid":803882,"ui